text: On the eval page, hovering over one of the links to an implementation ticket should display a hover tooltip of the ticket's full title

proposedTasks.title: Add hover tooltip to implementation ticket links on Eval page
proposedTasks.description:
In the Eval feedback feed, each feedback item displays links to mapped beads tasks (created_task_ids). When the user hovers over one of these ticket links, display a tooltip showing the ticket's full title.

Acceptance criteria:
- Hovering over any ticket link in the Eval feedback feed shows a tooltip with the ticket's full title (fetched via `bd show <id> --json`)
- Tooltip appears after a short delay (~200ms) and dismisses on mouse-out
- Tooltip is styled consistently with the app's design system (respects light/dark theme)
- If the title cannot be fetched (e.g., deleted ticket), the tooltip either does not appear or shows a graceful fallback
- No layout shift or flickering when tooltip appears/disappears

taskTitles: Add hover tooltip to implementation ticket links on Eval page
